snippet.title: Friedrich Nietzsche Quotes to Inspire You to Think Differently
snippet.description:
Friedrich Nietzsche Quotes to Inspire You to Think Differently. These are vivid sayings and quotes from Friedrich Nietzsche. The best quotes and aphorisms of Friedrich Nietzsche that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Friedrich Nietzsche are definitely worth your time.

Friedrich Wilhelm Nietzsche was a German philosopher, cultural critic and philologist whose work has exerted a profound influence on modern intellectual history. He began his career as a classical philologist before turning to philosophy.
